rComments: one of the nicest, kind prof at UTSC. Very very helpful. She is very understanding and sweet if you ever go to her with any issues. I love this prof and wished she taught more courses at utsc. Exams are a breeze, she gives alot of choice!
Doesnt clearly express what she expects from you in the course but just do the readings and you can easily receive an A in the class. Very nice teacher and tries to get to know the students by name.
